{
  "texts": [
    "DivorceBot simplifies the initial stages of divorce through a chatbot that offers personalised guidance and resources [73].",
    "OurFamilyWizard extends a comprehensive toolkit for co-parenting, featuring shared calendars, messaging, and expense tracking to improve relationship dynamics [74].",
    "Lex Machina introduces legal analytics to family law, enabling practitioners to form strategies based on insights into case trends and outcomes [75].",
    "Additionally, Modria stands out for its long-standing application in online dispute resolution within family law, employing data analysis and deductive reasoning to summarise disputes and propose resolutions [76].",
    "Collectively, these tools represent the forefront of applying AI and technology to streamline family law processes, reduce adversarial interactions, and promote effective resolution strategies."
  ]
